===Adjective===

#(Australia and New Zealand) Excellent. Exceptionally Good. Extraordinary. Fantastic. Great. Remarkable. Splendid. Super. Wonderful. Remarkable. Awesome (colloquial).


===Adverb===

#(Australia and New Zealand) Excellently. Exceptionally Well. Extraordinarily. Remarkably. Splendidly. Superlatively. Wonderfully. Awesomely (colloquial).


===Noun===

#(Australia and New Zealand) Something or someone that excites admiration by being extraordinarily good.
#(New South Wales) A type of apple.
#[(Surfing)] A type of [[surf board]] in the [[shortboard]] family called [[bonzer boards]]. 


